Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present, 2, 4, 6 & 6A  James Court, Tottenham, for sale. 
 
James Court presents an opportunity to purchase or lease a modern warehouse within an established industrial estate. To find buildings of this design and quality, occupiers typically have to settle to for an inferior location. Offering modern, high cubic capacity warehousing in an area typical of lower clearance warehouses. Glass facades with modern landscaping will ensure this property will be a shining light in a key city fringe industrial area. 
 
Location Benefits:
+ 150m* to Sunshine Road
+ 2km* to Sunshine Train Station
+ 5km* to Port of Melbourne
+ 7km* to Melbourne's CBD
+ 14km* to Tullamarine Airport
 
Property Highlights:
+ High clearance warehouse
+ Large yard and parking
+ Ample room to drop 40ft container in secure yard
+ Sliding gate and roller shutter door
+ Air conditioned office and amenities over two levels
+ Polished concrete lunch room

2 James Court, Tottenham - LEASED

4 James Court, Tottenham: LEASED

6 James Court, Tottenham - FOR SALE OR LEASE
+ Warehouse area: 697sqm*
+ Office & amenities: 133sqm*

6A James Court, Tottenham - FOR SALE OR LEASE
+ Warehouse area: 697sqm*
+ Office & amenities: 133sqm*

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.
